TUE 7/12 – Today’s show is in honor of “Cease & Alamo”, the famous duo from Biggie’s verse on “Get Money”. Oh wait…it’s not “Cease & Alamo”? Does Rich Homie Quan know that? I feel a HEE-HAW coming. Envy, Angela & Charlamagne also discuss the topic that terrorizes baby daddies worldwide: Would you let your baby momma’s new man kiss your son?!? Russell Wilson, we need you to come to the front of the congregation for a quick word.
